\[Ellipsis],n} in the fermionic Gaussian state characterized by n\[Times]n \
matrix grn of single-particle Green's function. "
    }],ExpressionUUID->"4ce5b367-3f4d-4f46-a970-683a520ae675"]},
   {"", Cell[TextData[{
     "WickLogarithmicNegativity[ws,",
