      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "22610963-eef3-4582-8594-b0e05f63e39f"],
     ",k2,\[Ellipsis]}]\[LineSeparator]calculates the logarithmic negativity \
for the Wick state (fermionic Gaussian pure state without pairing \
correlation) ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      StyleBox["ws", "TI"]], "InlineFormula",
      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
